Package: safetrain
Title: Reversible, ML-Safe Anonymization
Description: Key-based reversible anonymization of tabular data using a
  cryptographic key-derived orthogonal rotation (HMAC-PRNG + QR decomposition).
  All columns are encoded to numeric and transformed jointly; the rotation
  matrix and centering/scaling are derived from the secret key and never stored,
  so reversal requires the key. When two or more columns are anonymized, one
  column is dropped and encrypted, producing a reduced output.
Version: 0.1.0
